Proof of Theorem 1.: Consider the two groups \(b_{a}\in\mathcal{B}\) and \(b_{c}\in\mathcal{B}\) such that \(b_{a}\neq b_{c}\). Let \(d(b_{a},b_{c})\) be the difference in expected losses between the group \(b_{a}\) and \(b_{c}\):

